[
  {
    "startTime": 0.379,
    "endTime": 6.32,
    "text": "The following contains clips from Disney's Frozen and Frozen2 now available on Blu Ray and DVD."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.619,
    "endTime": 14.729,
    "text": "I was just wondering has another young woman, the queen perhaps, I don't know, passed through here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.739,
    "endTime": 17.2,
    "text": "Only one crazy enough to be out in this storm is you, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.52,
    "endTime": 27.1,
    "text": "You and this fellow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.1,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "Big summer blowout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 36.479,
    "text": "- Carrots. - Hah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.479,
    "endTime": 37.669,
    "text": "Behind you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.18,
    "endTime": 39.099,
    "text": "Oh, right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.11,
    "endTime": 40.299,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.4,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "A real howler in July, yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.11,
    "endTime": 46.7,
    "text": "Where ever could it be coming from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.7,
    "endTime": 48.650000000000006,
    "text": "The North Mountain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.65,
    "endTime": 49.708999999999996,
    "text": "The North Mountain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.43,
    "endTime": 51.77,
    "text": "That'll be 40."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.779,
    "endTime": 52.75,
    "text": "40?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.79,
    "endTime": 53.708999999999996,
    "text": "No, 10."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.72,
    "endTime": 54.08,
    "text": "Oh dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.09,
    "endTime": 54.77,
    "text": "That's no good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.779,
    "endTime": 58.93000000000001,
    "text": "See, this is from our winter stock, where supply and demand have a big problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.939,
    "endTime": 61.13,
    "text": "You want to talk about a supply and demand problem?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.139,
    "endTime": 62.580000000000005,
    "text": "I sell ice for a living."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.619,
    "endTime": 64.809,
    "text": "Oh, that's a rough business to be in right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.819,
    "endTime": 68.379,
    "text": "I mean that is really, that's unfortunate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.389,
    "endTime": 73.959,
    "text": "Still 40, but I will throw in a visit to Oaken's sauna. Hi family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.18,
    "endTime": 77.37,
    "text": "10's all I got."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.66,
    "endTime": 78.66,
    "text": "Help me out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.98,
    "endTime": 81.51,
    "text": "OK, we'll get you this and no more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.519,
    "endTime": 81.819,
    "text": "Ok."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.83,
    "endTime": 87.709,
    "text": "Just tell me one thing. What was happening on the North Mountain? Did it seem magical?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.709,
    "endTime": 88.269,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.91,
    "endTime": 95.0,
    "text": "Now, back up while I deal with this crook here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 97.37,
    "text": "What did you call me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.37,
    "endTime": 100.2,
    "text": "Ok. Ok. I'm-Ow! Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.2,
    "endTime": 103.91,
    "text": "Bye-bye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.91,
    "endTime": 105.19,
    "text": "Hey, you were right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.199,
    "endTime": 106.53999999999999,
    "text": "Just like a pillow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.05,
    "endTime": 110.11999999999999,
    "text": "I can't feel my legs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.18,
    "endTime": 111.77900000000001,
    "text": "I can't feel my legs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.309,
    "endTime": 114.599,
    "text": "Those are my legs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.099,
    "endTime": 115.68,
    "text": "Hey, do me a favor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.69,
    "endTime": 116.37899999999999,
    "text": "Grab my butt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.43,
    "endTime": 118.9,
    "text": "Oh, that feels better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.099,
    "endTime": 121.879,
    "text": "Hey, Sven. He found us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.089,
    "endTime": 123.78999999999999,
    "text": "Who's my cute little reindeer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.8,
    "endTime": 128.5,
    "text": "Don't talk to him like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.5,
    "endTime": 131.2,
    "text": "Here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.2,
    "endTime": 134.809,
    "text": "- You okay? - Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.809,
    "endTime": 135.399,
    "text": "How's your hair?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.77,
    "endTime": 138.8,
    "text": "It's fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.809,
    "endTime": 139.63,
    "text": "I'm good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.639,
    "endTime": 140.75900000000001,
    "text": "I've got a thick skull."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.77,
    "endTime": 144.47,
    "text": "I don't have a skull or bones."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.789,
    "endTime": 150.289,
    "text": "- So, so now what? - Now what? Now what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.889,
    "endTime": 153.649,
    "text": "Oh, what am I gonna do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.08,
    "endTime": 155.339,
    "text": "She threw me out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.58,
    "endTime": 158.13000000000002,
    "text": "I can't go back to Arundel with the weather like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.139,
    "endTime": 159.63000000000002,
    "text": "And then there's your ice business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.71,
    "endTime": 161.69,
    "text": "Don't worry about my ice business."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.559,
    "endTime": 163.69,
    "text": "Worry about your hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.699,
    "endTime": 164.19000000000003,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.419,
    "endTime": 165.449,
    "text": "I just fell off a cliff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.46,
    "endTime": 166.429,
    "text": "You should see your hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.44,
    "endTime": 168.72899999999998,
    "text": "- No, yours is turning white. -White?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.149,
    "endTime": 172.88,
    "text": "-It's what? -It's because she struck you, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.509,
    "endTime": 174.67899999999997,
    "text": "Does it look bad?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.259,
    "endTime": 177.79999999999998,
    "text": "-No. - You hesitated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.809,
    "endTime": 179.22,
    "text": "No, I didn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.24,
    "endTime": 180.61,
    "text": "Anna, you need help. Ok?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.61,
    "endTime": 181.199,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.21,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "Ok.Where are we going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 184.179,
    "text": "To see my friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.19,
    "endTime": 186.639,
    "text": "- The love experts? - Love experts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.66,
    "endTime": 186.929,
    "text": "Uh huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.2,
    "endTime": 189.79999999999998,
    "text": "And don't worry, they'll be able to fix this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.809,
    "endTime": 190.809,
    "text": "How do you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.309,
    "endTime": 194.169,
    "text": "Because I've seen them do it before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.41,
    "endTime": 198.04999999999998,
    "text": "I'd like to consider myself a love expert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.83,
    "endTime": 200.91000000000003,
    "text": "She's as cold as ice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.83,
    "endTime": 205.82000000000002,
    "text": "There is strange magic here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.83,
    "endTime": 206.5,
    "text": "Grand Pabbie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.5,
    "endTime": 208.089,
    "text": "Come, come, bring her to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.339,
    "endTime": 211.02,
    "text": "Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.339,
    "endTime": 213.339,
    "text": "Your life is in danger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.779,
    "endTime": 216.82999999999998,
    "text": "There is ice in your heart, put there by your sister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.32,
    "endTime": 222.279,
    "text": "If not removed, to solid ice will you freeze, forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.369,
    "endTime": 224.0,
    "text": "What? No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.0,
    "endTime": 225.25,
    "text": "But you can remove it, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.25,
    "endTime": 226.11,
    "text": "I cannot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.46,
    "endTime": 228.16,
    "text": "I'm sorry, Kristoff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.169,
    "endTime": 238.35000000000002,
    "text": "If it was her head that would be easy, but only an act of true love can thaw a frozen heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.36,
    "endTime": 246.88000000000002,
    "text": "A true love's kiss, perhaps?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.88,
    "endTime": 249.35,
    "text": "Anna, we've got to get you back to Hans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.35,
    "endTime": 249.94899999999998,
    "text": "Hans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.429,
    "endTime": 251.58,
    "text": "Pull us out, Sven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.91,
    "endTime": 253.19,
    "text": "Go ahead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.8,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "Ola. Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 257.179,
    "text": "I'm coming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.029,
    "endTime": 259.489,
    "text": "Let's go kiss Hans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.17,
    "endTime": 273.399,
    "text": "Who is this Hans?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.399,
    "endTime": 274.47,
    "text": "Just hang in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.66,
    "endTime": 283.70000000000005,
    "text": "Come on, buddy, faster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.0,
    "endTime": 285.549,
    "text": "I'll meet you guys at the castle!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.559,
    "endTime": 286.47,
    "text": "Stay out of sight, Olaf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.76,
    "endTime": 301.92,
    "text": "It's Princess Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.579,
    "endTime": 312.69,
    "text": "Are you gonna be okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.549,
    "endTime": 316.9,
    "text": "Don't worry about me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.9,
    "endTime": 323.279,
    "text": "Anna! Oh, you had us worried sick... - My lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.29,
    "endTime": 324.519,
    "text": "We will. Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.91,
    "endTime": 327.42,
    "text": "Make sure she's safe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.4,
    "endTime": 348.57899999999995,
    "text": "So where's Hans?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.619,
    "endTime": 349.85,
    "text": "What happened to your kiss?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.869,
    "endTime": 351.649,
    "text": "I was wrong about him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.029,
    "endTime": 354.0,
    "text": "It wasn't true love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.0,
    "endTime": 356.47,
    "text": "But we ran all the way here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.48,
    "endTime": 358.369,
    "text": "Please Olaf, you can't stay here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.739,
    "endTime": 359.549,
    "text": "You'll melt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.559,
    "endTime": 362.589,
    "text": "I am not leaving here until we find some other act of true love to save you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.559,
    "endTime": 365.059,
    "text": "Do you happen to have any ideas?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.7,
    "endTime": 367.72999999999996,
    "text": "I don't even know what love is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.859,
    "endTime": 368.64,
    "text": "That's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.649,
    "endTime": 374.41,
    "text": "I do. Love is putting someone else's needs before yours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.42,
    "endTime": 379.2,
    "text": "Like you know, how Kristoff brought you back here to Hans and left you forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.04,
    "endTime": 384.649,
    "text": "Kristoff loves me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.01,
    "endTime": 386.529,
    "text": "Wow. You really don't know anything about love, do you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.45,
    "endTime": 391.96999999999997,
    "text": "Olaf, you're melting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.2,
    "endTime": 394.30899999999997,
    "text": "Some people are worth melting for."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.64,
    "endTime": 401.28999999999996,
    "text": "Just maybe not right this second."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.959,
    "endTime": 405.13,
    "text": "Don't worry, I've got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.989,
    "endTime": 409.339,
    "text": "We're gonna get through it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.35,
    "endTime": 410.779,
    "text": "Oh, wait, hang on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.79,
    "endTime": 411.73,
    "text": "I'm getting something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.5,
    "endTime": 415.38,
    "text": "It's Kristoff and Sven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.39,
    "endTime": 416.90999999999997,
    "text": "They're coming back this way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.149,
    "endTime": 418.69,
    "text": "They are?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.7,
    "endTime": 419.38,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.39,
    "endTime": 421.32,
    "text": "He's really moving fast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.519,
    "endTime": 422.779,
    "text": "I guess I was wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.809,
    "endTime": 425.38000000000005,
    "text": "I guess Kristoff doesn't love you enough to leave you behind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.7,
    "endTime": 426.96999999999997,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.869,
    "endTime": 429.079,
    "text": "OK. Ok. Here I come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.459,
    "endTime": 431.69,
    "text": "- Oh. - Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.059,
    "endTime": 433.519,
    "text": "OK. OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.519,
    "endTime": 434.6,
    "text": "Here we are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.609,
    "endTime": 439.279,
    "text": "Oh, I owe you a sled."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.91,
    "endTime": 443.809,
    "text": "Are you serious?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.619,
    "endTime": 445.89000000000004,
    "text": "And it's the latest model."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.029,
    "endTime": 447.75,
    "text": "No, I can't accept this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.76,
    "endTime": 450.7,
    "text": "You have to. No returns, no exchanges. Queen's orders."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.7,
    "endTime": 454.829,
    "text": "She's named you the official Arundel Ice Master and Deliverer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.839,
    "endTime": 455.95,
    "text": "What? That's not a thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.95,
    "endTime": 456.829,
    "text": "Oh, sure it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.839,
    "endTime": 458.769,
    "text": "And it even has a cup holder."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.339,
    "endTime": 460.179,
    "text": "Do you like it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.19,
    "endTime": 460.92,
    "text": "Like it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.339,
    "endTime": 462.36899999999997,
    "text": "I love it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.239,
    "endTime": 464.839,
    "text": "I could kiss you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.17,
    "endTime": 470.63,
    "text": "I could, I mean, I'd like to. May I? We me? I mean, may we? Wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.64,
    "endTime": 471.07,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.309,
    "endTime": 473.17900000000003,
    "text": "We may."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.279,
    "endTime": 482.029,
    "text": "I'm tired too and Sven promised to read me a bedtime story, didn't you, Sven?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.589,
    "endTime": 483.059,
    "text": "Did I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.29,
    "endTime": 485.98900000000003,
    "text": "Oh, you do the best voices."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.0,
    "endTime": 491.7,
    "text": "Like when you pretend to be Kristoff, and you're like \"I just need to go talk to some rocks about my childhood and stuff.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.79,
    "endTime": 494.72,
    "text": "How about you guys start without me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.76,
    "endTime": 503.75,
    "text": "Did Elsa seem weird to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.76,
    "endTime": 507.0,
    "text": "She seemed like Elsa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.0,
    "endTime": 510.2,
    "text": "That last word really seemed to throw her. What was it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.2,
    "endTime": 510.95,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.369,
    "endTime": 512.659,
    "text": "I don't, I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.669,
    "endTime": 514.9689999999999,
    "text": "- But... - Ah, ice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.0,
    "endTime": 516.539,
    "text": "Oh, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.549,
    "endTime": 518.9399999999999,
    "text": "She couldn't act up ice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.95,
    "endTime": 520.21,
    "text": "I better go check on her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.51,
    "endTime": 524.609,
    "text": "Thanks, honey. Love you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.609,
    "endTime": 525.4290000000001,
    "text": "Love you too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.59,
    "endTime": 528.25,
    "text": "It's fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.7,
    "endTime": 530.82,
    "text": "They're both asleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 531.78,
    "endTime": 535.8,
    "text": "So, what do you want to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.0,
    "endTime": 542.6,
    "text": "Sven, keep us steady, will ya?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.6,
    "endTime": 543.21,
    "text": "Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.88,
    "endTime": 544.26,
    "text": "Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.559,
    "endTime": 550.4689999999999,
    "text": "Remember our first trip like this when I said you'd have to be crazy to want to marry a man you just met."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.479,
    "endTime": 552.0300000000001,
    "text": "Wait, what? Crazy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.15,
    "endTime": 553.3,
    "text": "You didn't say I was crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.34,
    "endTime": 554.789,
    "text": "You think I'm crazy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.799,
    "endTime": 556.4689999999999,
    "text": "No. I did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.479,
    "endTime": 559.3090000000001,
    "text": "You were. Not crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.32,
    "endTime": 563.2,
    "text": "Clearly, just naive. Not naive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.21,
    "endTime": 570.599,
    "text": "Just, new to love like, like I was and when you're new, you're bound to get it wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.609,
    "endTime": 572.729,
    "text": "So you're saying I'm wrong for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.739,
    "endTime": 573.25,
    "text": "What? No, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.0,
    "endTime": 585.95,
    "text": "The dam. It still stands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.729,
    "endTime": 588.789,
    "text": "It was in Grand Pabbie's visions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.719,
    "endTime": 590.859,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.869,
    "endTime": 592.9,
    "text": "I don't know but it's still in good shape."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.909,
    "endTime": 593.9,
    "text": "Thank goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.929,
    "endTime": 594.6999999999999,
    "text": "What do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.929,
    "endTime": 600.4,
    "text": "Well, if that dam broke, it would send a tidal wave so big it would wash away everything on this fjord."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.4,
    "endTime": 604.5,
    "text": "Everything? But Arundel's on this fjord."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.51,
    "endTime": 606.78,
    "text": "Nothing's gonna happen to Arundel, Anna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.789,
    "endTime": 607.7189999999999,
    "text": "It's gonna be fine. Come here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.0,
    "endTime": 623.0,
    "text": "You know, under different circumstances, this would be a pretty romantic place, don't you think?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.0,
    "endTime": 625.299,
    "text": "Different circumstances? You mean like with someone else?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.299,
    "endTime": 625.6899999999999,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.7,
    "endTime": 630.0490000000001,
    "text": "No, no. I'm saying just in case we don't make it out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.059,
    "endTime": 630.89,
    "text": "Wait, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.9,
    "endTime": 632.39,
    "text": "You don't think we're gonna make it out of here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.4,
    "endTime": 635.26,
    "text": "No, no, I mean, no, we will make it out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.27,
    "endTime": 640.63,
    "text": "- Well, technically, the odds are kind of complicated but my point is in case we die. - You think we're gonna die?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.64,
    "endTime": 645.1,
    "text": "No, no, no, no, we will die at some point. Not at any recent time. - Where's Elsa. I swore that I wouldn't leave her side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.299,
    "endTime": 648.2289999999999,
    "text": "But way far in the future we will die. - Elsa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.51,
    "endTime": 653.489,
    "text": "Don't patronize me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.76,
    "endTime": 656.099,
    "text": "There is one more thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.0,
    "endTime": 662.25,
    "text": "Anna, you are the most extraordinary person I've ever known."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.25,
    "endTime": 664.27,
    "text": "I love you with all I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 665.26,
    "endTime": 668.7,
    "text": "Will you marry me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668.7,
    "endTime": 670.21,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 686.169,
    "endTime": 691.3199999999999,
    "text": "Presenting Her Majesty, Queen Anna of Arendelle!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.619,
    "endTime": 703.539,
    "text": "Hello, hi. Sven, don't you look nice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.989,
    "endTime": 706.5,
    "text": "Oh, my goodness. Olaf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706.5,
    "endTime": 709.28,
    "text": "Charmed, I'm sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.28,
    "endTime": 710.53,
    "text": "Charming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 710.539,
    "endTime": 714.619,
    "text": "Your majesty. - Kristoff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.84,
    "endTime": 718.39,
    "text": "Oh. Did you boys get all dressed up for me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.39,
    "endTime": 719.809,
    "text": "It was Sven's idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720.559,
    "endTime": 721.419,
    "text": "One hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.96,
    "endTime": 723.469,
    "text": "You get this for one hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.479,
    "endTime": 724.2,
    "text": "That's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.4,
    "endTime": 727.159,
    "text": "I prefer you in leather anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.099,
    "endTime": 734.26,
    "text": "I'm shocked you can last an hour. That was brutal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.26,
    "endTime": 736.2,
    "text": "The things we do for love."
  }
]